  "instructions": [
    "Score the skin of the snapper fish and marinate it in a mixture of fermented fish paste, garlic, chili flakes, lime juice, olive oil, salt, and black pepper for 30 minutes.",
    "Prepare a ssam-wrap by cutting it open to create a large shell with a flat bottom and a delicate top.",
    "After marinating, grill the snapper fish for 3-4 minutes per side or until it's cooked through and flakes easily with a fork.",
    "Spoon the grilled snapper fish into the ssam-wrap shell, followed by a spoonful of avocado, red onion, and fresh cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
